    Configurable, Serializable, Classifier, AWTRenderable, Learner<Example<Instance>>, MOAObject, OptionHandler
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    MultilabelHoeffdingTree

    public class HoeffdingTreeClassifLeaves
extends HoeffdingTree
    Hoeffding Tree that have a classifier at the leaves. A Hoeffding tree is an incremental, anytime decision tree induction algorithm that is capable of learning from massive data streams, assuming that the distribution generating examples does not change over time.
